Description: Both a cloud and a puppy, CLOUD PUPPY is an anxious but excitable little scamp who is excited to learn what her friends are into!
A great friend and a chill hang, BERRY ROSE is a teddy bear but also a unicorn but also a fairy.
The thing about MOSSQUATCH is even though he's super big he's also quite gentle and nice. He also has no neck, his head just kinda sits right in the middle of his shoulders.
JACK is pretty much just a deer, but as the oldest and bravest of the gang he ends up getting everyone to do what he wants to.
